quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  92,15,La yaslaha illelﾂｴeﾅ殘a
  92,16,Elleziy kezzebe ve tevella
  92,17,Ve seyﾃｼcennebﾃｼhelﾂｴetka
  92,18,Elleziy yﾃｼﾂｴtiy malehu yetezekka
  92,19,Ve ma liehadin ﾂｴﾄｱndehu min nﾄｱﾂｴmetin tﾃｼcza
  92,20,ﾄｰllebtiﾄ歛e vechi rabbihilﾂｴaﾂｴla
  92,21,Ve lesevfe yerda
  93,1,Vedduha
  93,2,Velleyli iza seca
  93,3,Ma veddeﾂｴake rabbﾃｼke ve ma kala
  93,4,Ve lelﾂｴahﾄｱretﾃｼ hayrﾃｼn leke minelﾂｴula
  93,5,Ve lesevfe yuﾂｴtﾄｱyke rabbﾃｼke feterda
  93,6,Elem yecidke yetiymen feava
  93,7,Ve vecedeke dallen feheda
  93,8,Ve vecedeke ﾂｴailen feaﾄ殤a
  93,9,Femmel yetiyme fela takher
  93,10,Ve emmessaile fela tenher
  93,11,Ve emma binﾄｱﾂｴmeti rabbike fehaddis
  94,1,Elem neﾅ殲ah leke sadrek
  94,2,Ve vadaﾂｴna ﾂｴanke vizreke
  94,3,Elleziy enkada zahreke
  94,4,Ve refaﾂｴna leke zikreke
  94,5,Feinne meﾂｴalﾂｴusri yﾃｼsren
  94,6,ﾄｰnne meﾂｴalﾂｴusri yﾃｼsren
  94,7,Feiza feraﾄ殳e fensab
  94,8,Ve ila rabbike ferﾄ歛b